<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托小心地带着会说话的木头回到了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托的家干净整洁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在一个大房间里，有一张床，一张桌子，一些工具和一个火炉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然杰佩托努力工作，但他并没有太多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，杰佩托并不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我该从哪里开始呢？”他自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可从来没有做过小男孩儿呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从腿开始吧！这样我就可以跑得很快了！”木头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我觉得你应该先有眼睛，这样你才不会撞到墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不希望你受伤。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托可以做自己的孩子，他感到非常开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他先雕刻出脸，接着雕刻出眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当脸逐渐成形，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托开始兴奋地想象自己可以和小男孩儿一起做的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在一起会多么地开心呀！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，你的眼睛看上去很灵活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你看得清楚吗？”杰佩托问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊，太糟糕了！”木头大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”杰佩托担心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他以为木头什么也看不见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们太穷了！看看这个小房间！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想要变富，不是穷。”木头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听到小男孩儿为他的家感到羞愧，杰佩托觉得非常伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他下定决心，小男孩儿需要的，他一定全都给。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我接下来会雕刻出你的耳朵，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样你就可以听和学习。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托专心地工作了一整天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在午饭前雕刻了头发，鼻子和笑脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他和小男孩儿一起分着吃了第一顿饭，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们吃了面包和奶酪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小男孩儿，我们在一起一定会非常开心。”杰佩托边吃边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他撕下一点面包，放进小男孩儿的嘴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是我不应该叫你‘小男孩儿’。你应该有个名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我应该叫你什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道了！你可以叫我大森林里的王子艾德蒙。”木头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他喜欢这个名字，因为听上去很大很重要。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对一个小男孩儿来说，这个名字太大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你是木头做成的，我叫你匹诺曹，怎么样？”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想要起一个小男孩儿会喜欢的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的。匹诺曹，听上去像是一个很重要的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然没有大森林里的王子艾德蒙那么好，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我觉得还不错。”他答应了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！那就定匹诺曹了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了庆祝，我来雕刻你的手臂和双腿，这样我们就能跳舞了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托快速地雕刻着木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托一完成匹诺曹的腿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹就跳到地上，从前门跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”杰佩托喊道，“匹诺曹，你要去哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去探险！”匹诺曹大声回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你还没有衣服呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没穿衣服怎么可以跑走呢！不要走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托一边追着匹诺曹，一边大声喊着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，杰佩托忘记把他的刀放在桌子上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他手拿着刀，追赶着匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邻居们以为杰佩托要伤害匹诺曹，就喊了警察：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警察！警察！快抓住他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个警察就在附近，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到街上，刚好抓住了杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不给杰佩托解释的机会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察很怕杰佩托的刀，当天晚上他就把杰佩托关进了监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>